your session. You switched accounts on another tab or window. Reload to refresh your session. Dismiss alert\n\n[dandavison](/dandavison) / **[delta](/dandavison/delta)** Public\n\n-   [Notifications](/login?return_to=%2Fdandavison%2Fdelta) You must be signed in to change notification settings\n-   [Fork 547](/login?return_to=%2Fdandavison%2Fdelta)\n-   [Star 31.4k](/login?return_to=%2Fdandavison%2Fdelta)\n    \n\n-   [Code](/dandavison/delta)\n-   [Issues 302](/dandavison/delta/issues)\n-   [Pull requests 101](/dandavison/delta/pulls)\n-   [Discussions](/dandavison/delta/discussions)\n-   [Actions](/dandavison/delta/actions)\n-   [Projects](/dandavison/delta/projects)\n-   [Security and quality 0](/dandavison/delta/security)\n-   [Insights](/dandavison/delta/pulse)\n\nAdditional navigation options\n\n-   [Code](/dandavison/delta)\n-   [Issues](/dandavison/delta/issues)\n-   [Pull requests](/dandavison/delta/pulls)\n-   [Discussions](/dandavison/delta/discussions)\n-   [Actions](/dandavison/delta/actions)\n-   [Projects](/dandavison/delta/projects)\n-   [Security and quality](/dandavison/delta/security)\n-   [Insights](/dandavison/delta/pulse)\n\n [](/dandavison/delta)\n\n# dandavison/delta\n\n main\n\n[Branches](/dandavison/delta/branches)[Tags](/dandavison/delta/tags)\n\n[](/dandavison/delta/branches)[](/dandavison/delta/tags)\n\nGo to file\n\nCode\n\nOpen more actions menu\n\n## Folders and files\n\nName\n\nName\n\nLast commit message\n\nLast commit date\n\n## Latest commit\n\n## History\n\n[2,176 Commits](/dandavison/delta/commits/main/)\n\n[](/dandavison/delta/commits/main/)2,176 Commits\n\n[.cargo](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/.cargo \".cargo\")\n\n[.cargo](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/.cargo \".cargo\")\n\n[.github](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/.github \".github\")\n\n[.github](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/.github \".github\")\n\n[etc](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/etc \"etc\")\n\n[etc](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/etc \"etc\")\n\n[manual](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/manual \"manual\")\n\n[manual](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/manual \"manual\")\n\n[src](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/src \"src\")\n\n[src](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/src \"src\")\n\n[tests](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/tests \"tests\")\n\n[tests](/dandavison/delta/tree/main/tests \"tests\")\n\n[.gitattributes](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/.gitattributes \".gitattributes\")\n\n[.gitattributes](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/.gitattributes \".gitattributes\")\n\n[.gitignore](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/.gitignore \".gitignore\")\n\n[.gitignore](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/.gitignore \".gitignore\")\n\n[ARCHITECTURE.md](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/ARCHITECTURE.md \"ARCHITECTURE.md\")\n\n[ARCHITECTURE.md](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/ARCHITECTURE.md \"ARCHITECTURE.md\")\n\n[CONTRIBUTING.md](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md \"CONTRIBUTING.md\")\n\n[CONTRIBUTING.md](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md \"CONTRIBUTING.md\")\n\n[Cargo.lock](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/Cargo.lock \"Cargo.lock\")\n\n[Cargo.lock](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/Cargo.lock \"Cargo.lock\")\n\n[Cargo.toml](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/Cargo.toml \"Cargo.toml\")\n\n[Cargo.toml](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/Cargo.toml \"Cargo.toml\")\n\n[LICENSE](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/LICENSE \"LICENSE\")\n\n[LICENSE](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/LICENSE \"LICENSE\")\n\n[Makefile](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/Makefile \"Makefile\")\n\n[Makefile](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/Makefile \"Makefile\")\n\n[README.md](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/README.md \"README.md\")\n\n[README.md](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/README.md \"README.md\")\n\n[themes.gitconfig](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/themes.gitconfig \"themes.gitconfig\")\n\n[themes.gitconfig](/dandavison/delta/blob/main/themes.gitconfig \"themes.gitconfig\")\n\nView all files\n\n## Repository files navigation\n\n-   [README](#)\n-   [Contributing](#)\n-   [MIT license](#)\n\nMore items\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/147996902-9829bd3f-cd33-466e-833e-49a6f3ebd623.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/147996902-9829bd3f-cd33-466e-833e-49a6f3ebd623.png)\n\n [![CI](https://github.com/dandavison/delta/workflows/Continuous%20Integration/badge.svg)](https://github.com/dandavison/delta/actions)[![Coverage Status](https://camo.githubusercontent.com/1a33a9bbbddfc2934c5ba71c152f9361ed374559d8c2e8987b13cab69fae2f74/68747470733a2f2f636f766572616c6c732e696f2f7265706f732f6769746875622f64616e64617669736f6e2f64656c74612f62616467652e7376673f6272616e63683d6d61696e) ](https://coveralls.io/github/dandavison/delta?branch=main)[![Gitter](https://camo.githubusercontent.com/4d75e0aa464916884ffd560878ff2cb0103c11c36087da05817a12d5dde34186/68747470733a2f2f6261646765732e6769747465722e696d2f64616e64617669736f6e2d64656c74612f636f6d6d756e6974792e737667)](https://gitter.im/dandavison-delta/community?utm_source=badge&utm_medium=badge&utm_campaign=pr-badge)\n\n## Get Started\n\n[](#get-started)\n\n[Install it](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/installation.html) (the package is called \"git-delta\" in most package managers, but the executable is just `delta`) and add this to your `~/.gitconfig`:\n\n\\[core\\]\n    pager \\= delta\n\n\\[interactive\\]\n    diffFilter \\= delta \\--color-only\n\n\\[delta\\]\n    navigate \\= true  # use n and N to move between diff sections\n    dark \\= true      # or light = true, or omit for auto-detection\n\n\\[merge\\]\n    conflictStyle \\= zdiff3\n\nOr run:\n\ngit config --global core.pager delta\ngit config --global interactive.diffFilter 'delta --color-only'\ngit config --global delta.navigate true\ngit config --global delta.dark true  # or \\`delta.light true\\`, or omit for auto-detection\ngit config --global merge.conflictStyle zdiff3\n\nDelta has many features and is very customizable; please see `delta -h` (short help) or `delta --help` (full manual), or the [online user manual](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/).\n\n## Features\n\n[](#features)\n\n-   Language syntax highlighting with the same syntax-highlighting themes as [bat](https://github.com/sharkdp/bat#readme)\n-   Word-level diff highlighting using a Levenshtein edit inference algorithm\n-   Side-by-side view with line-wrapping\n-   Line numbering\n-   `n` and `N` keybindings to move between files in large diffs, and between diffs in `log -p` views (`--navigate`)\n-   Improved merge conflict display\n-   Improved `git blame` display (syntax highlighting; `--hyperlinks` formats commits as links to hosting provider etc. Supported hosting providers are: GitHub, GitLab, SourceHut, Codeberg)\n-   Syntax-highlights grep output from `rg`, `git grep`, `grep`, etc\n-   Support for Git's `--color-moved` feature.\n-   Code can be copied directly from the diff (`-/+` markers are removed by default).\n-   `diff-highlight` and `diff-so-fancy` emulation modes\n-   Commit hashes can be formatted as terminal [hyperlinks](https://gist.github.com/egmontkob/eb114294efbcd5adb1944c9f3cb5feda) to the hosting provider page (`--hyperlinks`). File paths can also be formatted as hyperlinks for opening in your OS.\n-   Stylable box/line decorations to draw attention to commit, file and hunk header sections.\n-   Style strings (foreground color, background color, font attributes) are supported for >20 stylable elements, using the same color/style language as git\n-   Handles traditional unified diff output in addition to git output\n-   Automatic detection of light/dark terminal background\n\n## A syntax-highlighting pager for git, diff, and grep output\n\n[](#a-syntax-highlighting-pager-for-git-diff-and-grep-output)\n\nCode evolves, and we all spend time studying diffs. Delta aims to make this both efficient and enjoyable: it allows you to make extensive changes to the layout and styling of diffs, as well as allowing you to stay arbitrarily close to the default git/diff output.\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/86275526-76792100-bba1-11ea-9e78-6be9baa80b29.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/86275526-76792100-bba1-11ea-9e78-6be9baa80b29.png)  \n\ndelta with `line-numbers` activated\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/87230973-412eb900-c381-11ea-8aec-cc200290bd1b.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/87230973-412eb900-c381-11ea-8aec-cc200290bd1b.png)  \n\ndelta with `side-by-side` and `line-numbers` activated\n\nHere's what `git show` can look like with git configured to use delta:\n\n  \n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/81058545-a5725f80-8e9c-11ea-912e-d21954586a44.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/81058545-a5725f80-8e9c-11ea-912e-d21954586a44.png)\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/81058911-6abcf700-8e9d-11ea-93be-e212824ec03d.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/81058911-6abcf700-8e9d-11ea-93be-e212824ec03d.png)\n\n\"Dracula\" theme\n\n\"GitHub\" theme\n\n  \n  \n\n### Syntax-highlighting themes\n\n[](#syntax-highlighting-themes)\n\n**All the syntax-highlighting color themes that are available with [bat](https://github.com/sharkdp/bat/) are available with delta:**\n\n  \n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/149431273-e3ad049d-771e-4186-869d-0e57967958a6.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/149431273-e3ad049d-771e-4186-869d-0e57967958a6.png)\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/149431419-48836001-2afc-4fd0-97ad-561a69b71db7.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/149431419-48836001-2afc-4fd0-97ad-561a69b71db7.png)\n\n`delta --show-syntax-themes --dark`\n\n`delta --show-syntax-themes --light`\n\n  \n\n### Side-by-side view\n\n[](#side-by-side-view)\n\n\\[[User manual](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/side-by-side-view.html)\\]\n\n\\[delta\\]\n    side-by-side \\= true\n\nBy default, side-by-side view has line-numbers activated, and has syntax highlighting in both the left and right panels: \\[[config](#side-by-side-view-1)\\]\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/87230973-412eb900-c381-11ea-8aec-cc200290bd1b.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/87230973-412eb900-c381-11ea-8aec-cc200290bd1b.png)\n\nSide-by-side view wraps long lines automatically:\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/139064537-f8479504-16d3-429a-b4f6-d0122438adaa.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/139064537-f8479504-16d3-429a-b4f6-d0122438adaa.png)\n\n### Line numbers\n\n[](#line-numbers)\n\n\\[[User manual](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/line-numbers.html)\\]\n\n\\[delta\\]\n    line-numbers \\= true\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/86275526-76792100-bba1-11ea-9e78-6be9baa80b29.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/86275526-76792100-bba1-11ea-9e78-6be9baa80b29.png)\n\n### Merge conflicts\n\n[](#merge-conflicts)\n\n\\[[User manual](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/merge-conflicts.html)\\]\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/144783121-bb549100-69d8-41b8-ac62-1704f1f7b43e.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/144783121-bb549100-69d8-41b8-ac62-1704f1f7b43e.png)\n\n### Git blame\n\n[](#git-blame)\n\n\\[[User manual](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/git-blame.html)\\]\n\n[![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/141891376-1fdb87dc-1d9c-4ad6-9d72-eeb19a8aeb0b.png)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/141891376-1fdb87dc-1d9c-4ad6-9d72-eeb19a8aeb0b.png)\n\n### Ripgrep, git grep\n\n[](#ripgrep-git-grep)\n\n\\[[User manual](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/grep.html)\\]\n\n[![image](https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/242993705-d203d380-5acb-4296-aeb9-e38c73d6c27f.png?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..vzOr1fNNUNgXVMgA7Uq8A8Z6-IukQAKemdPwUa9WZiw)](https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/52205/242993705-d203d380-5acb-4296-aeb9-e38c73d6c27f.png?jwt=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..vzOr1fNNUNgXVMgA7Uq8A8Z6-IukQAKemdPwUa9WZiw)\n\n### Installation and usage\n\n[](#installation-and-usage)\n\nPlease see the [user manual](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/) and `delta --help`.\n\n### Maintainers\n\n[](#maintainers)\n\n-   [@dandavison](https://github.com/dandavison)\n-   [@th1000s](https://github.com/th1000s)\n\n## About\n\nA syntax-highlighting pager for git, diff, grep, rg --json, and blame output\n\n[dandavison.github.io/delta/](https://dandavison.github.io/delta/ \"https://dandavison.github.io/delta/\")\n\n### Topics\n\n[git](/topics/git \"Topic: git\") [rust](/topics/rust \"Topic: rust\") [diff](/topics/diff \"Topic: diff\") [delta](/topics/delta \"Topic: delta\") [pager](/topics/pager \"Topic: pager\") [syntax-highlighter](/topics/syntax-highlighter \"Topic: syntax-highlighter\") [color-themes](/topics/color-themes \"Topic: color-themes\") [git-delta](/topics/git-delta \"Topic: git-delta\")\n\n### Resources\n\n[Readme](#readme-ov-file)\n\n### License\n\n[MIT license](#MIT-1-ov-file)\n\n### Contributing\n\n[Contributing](#contributing-ov-file)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n[Activity](/dandavison/delta/activity)\n\n### Stars\n\n**31.4k** stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n**111** watching\n\n### Forks\n\n[**547** forks](/dandavison/delta/forks)\n\n[Report repository](/contact/report-content?content_url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdandavison%2Fdelta&report=dandavison+%28user%29)\n\n## [Releases 62](/dandavison/delta/releases)\n\n[\n\n0.19.2 Latest\n\nMar 28, 2026\n\n\n\n](/dandavison/delta/releases/tag/0.19.2)\n\n[\\+ 61 releases](/dandavison/delta/releases)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n## [Contributors](/dandavison/delta/graphs/contributors)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n## Languages\n\n-   [Rust 95.6%](/dandavison/delta/search?l=rust)\n-   [Shell 4.1%](/dandavison/delta/search?l=shell)\n-   Other 0.3%\n\n## Footer\n\n[](https://github.com)© 2026 GitHub, Inc.\n\n### Footer navigation\n\n-   [Terms](https://docs.github.com/site-policy/github-terms/github-terms-of-service)\n-   [Privacy](https://docs.github.com/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement)\n-   [Security](https://github.com/security)\n-   [Status](https://www.githubstatus.com/)\n-   [Community](https://github.community/)\n-   [Docs](https://docs.github.com/)\n-   [Contact](https://support.github.com?tags=dotcom-footer)\n-   Manage cookies\n-   Do not share my personal information\n\nYou can’t perform that action at this time.","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"https://github.com/dandavison/delta (text/html; charset=utf-8)","time":{"start":1783944286884,"end":1783944287528}},"id":"prt_f5b5d901f0013AUQFp2rDskZYe","sessionID":"ses_0a4a439a4ffe52Yfhj76CZK3oI","messageID":"msg_f5b5d7178001HHwZXNjiHzoAO3"}}
