capability tier classification are all new to this packet.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Which canonical representation and extraction pipeline best preserve semantic structure across formats?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1: Which canonical representation and extraction pipeline best preserve semantic structure across formats?\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Direct format-to-format comparison without canonical intermediate\",\"reason\":\"Combinatorial N×M adapter explosion; hub-and-spoke model is sustainable\",\"evidence\":\"Iteration analysis of N format pairs\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-13T14:10:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000}' >> \"$ARTIFACT_DIR/deep-research-state.jsonl\"","time":{"start":1783944397292,"end":1783944397302}},"id":"prt_f5b5f3572001O18fmxLYqjOsar","sessionID":"ses_0a4a439a4ffe52Yfhj76CZK3oI","messageID":"msg_f5b5f2407001UQCNTRLNoWbFel"}}
