face, dependency set, and standalone-skill workflow best suit v1?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q5: Which runtime, portable interface, dependency set, and standalone-skill workflow best suit v1?\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-13T14:30:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":7,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Security constraints for untrusted document input\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.8,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Layered defense model, format-specific threat vectors, DOMPurify integration, XML bomb protection, and encrypted document handling are novel security synthesis.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"What security constraints apply to handling untrusted DOCX, HTML, and PDF input?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q7: What security constraints apply to handling untrusted DOCX, HTML, and PDF input?\"],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-13T14:35:00Z\",\"durationMs\":300000}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":8,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Architecture shape comparison and eliminated alternatives\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":0.6,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Formal comparison of three architecture shapes with eliminated alternatives record documented with evidence.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Compare at least three architecture shapes and record eliminated alternatives\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Browser-first SPA\",\"reason\":\"Cannot support automatic snapshot lifecycle or CLI/skill integration; browser storage is ephemeral\",\"evidence\":\"Architecture analysis against P0 requirements\"},{\"approach\":\"Electron/Tauri desktop application\",\"reason\":\"Excessive dependency weight for CLI-first use case; distribution complexity disproportionate to value\",\"evidence\":\"Architecture analysis against P0 requirements\"},{\"approach\":\"Python-only implementation\",\"reason\":\"Lacks unified.js AST ecosystem; two-language complexity for HTML report generation\",\"evidence\":\"Runtime comparison in iteration 6\"},{\"approach\":\"